    "It is extremely concerning when such attacks target high-profile individuals.",
    "Moreover, generative AI enhances the ability to profile patients, thereby increasing the risk of privacy violations and attacks, although this capability is not unique to AI.In addition to AI-specific security and privacy threats, AI systems interfacing with other hardware and software may face new security and privacy threats that have never existed before [57].",
